Almost 20 years after making their iconic turn as Miranda, Andy, Emily and Nigelâ€”Meryl Streep, Anne Hathaway, Emily Blunt and Stanley Tucci return to the fashionable streets of New York City and the sleek offices of Runway Magazine in the eagerly awaited sequel to the 2006 phenomenon that defined a generation.

â€œThe Devil Wears Prada 2â€ is produced by Wendy Finerman, and executive produced by Michael Bederman, Karen Rosenfelt and Aline Brosh McKenna. The film debuts exclusively in theaters May 1.

videos.title: WWE 2K26: Gameplay Trailer Breakdown! New Details, Hidden Features, Showcase Matches & More!
videos.description:
Join us as we breakdown the new WWE 2K26 Gameplay Trailer to reveal of the new content it includes, secrets and hidden features!

The new gameplay trailer features a ton of new footage including the first look at Inferno match gameplay featuring The Undertaker and Kane, Dumpster match gameplay between Michin and Chelsea Green, and new footage of the Scrapyard Brawl area coming to The Island!

Also shown in the trailer were some of the new gameplay features including the return of stackable tables, the new match start feature, barricade brawls, and the new bag of thumbtacks!

The trailer also revealed the addition of a classic version of CM Punk featuring his ROH / TNA gear, with this further adding to the speculation of Steve Corino joining the roster as a new ECW Legend!

What did you think of the trailer? Did you catch anything I missed?
Let me know your thoughts in the comments!

videos.description: Ribald, tasteless and hilarious ... this classic spoof of the Western genre by director Mel Brooks pokes fun at everyone and everything. A corrupt governor grants a reprieve to an African American convict if the condemned man agrees to serve as sheriff of a small Western town, believing that new sheriff will only live long enough to serve the needs of the governor and his nefarious railroad-baron backer. Academy Award nominations for Best Actress in a Supporting Role (Madeline Kahn); Best Music, Original Song; and Best Film Editing.
